_aChangeLog.text: Blends, bugs fixed, better detail, moved CT spawn to the bombtarget

_aLatestUpdates._sText: UPDATE: Fixed alot of bugs. Made some more stuff in the old CT Spawn (Removed it to inside the house(bombtarget))
In this version, I named the map hoejhus\_undead instead of hoejhus9\_undead. I changed alot of bugs. Me and some friends used about an hour to find and fix bugs in the map.

_sText:
Update:
==================
### Fixed alot of bugs. Made some more stuff in the old CT Spawn (Removed it to inside the house(bombtarget), and added new pictures!)

Hi. I made this map, for my friends community [Undead.dk](http://undead.dk/ "")
It will be played on his WCS and RPG server.

I was inspired of the normal [hoejhus9](http://css.gamebanana.com/maps/68885 "") and [TopHATTwaffles](http://gamebanana.com/members/144386 "")[Hammer Tutorial #50](http://www.tophattwaffle.com/hammer-tutorial-50-d-perfectly-lining-up-3d-skyboxes/ ""), but made the map from scratch, and as you can see, it is very different from the normal [hoejhus9](http://css.gamebanana.com/maps/68885 "")

Thanks to:
------------------
[RadioBob](http://gamebanana.com/members/929644 "") for his [Old House](http://dods.gamebanana.com/prefabs/4906 "") Prefab. It is used for the bomb target. (You need to go the bathroom at 1. floor, to plant the bomb)

Have fun, please rate and tell me what you think :)
==================
